{"hash":"b5204168a060386a9f73679206722474616dae4b","data":{"page":{"title":"Parties","content":"<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\">Parties</h3>\n<p>We provide mobile disco services for birthday&nbsp;parties, anniversaries, retirement and leaving parties, dedicated decade nights, etc.<br />\nAt all parties we will supply a sound system appropriate to your needs and run it at volumes that meet your requirements. Because we use intelligent lighting, which is totally controllable, You can rest assured that if you do not want wildly flashing light you don&#8217;t have to have them.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.arcdisco.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/Furnex-Pelham-Village-hall-1.jpg\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-478\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-478 size-medium\" title=\"Furnex Pelham Village hall\" src=\"https://www.arcdisco.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/Furnex-Pelham-Village-hall-1-300x200.jpg\" alt=\"Furnex Pelham Village hall 1\" width=\"300\" height=\"200\" srcset=\"https://www.arcdisco.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/Furnex-Pelham-Village-hall-1-300x200.jpg 300w, https://www.arcdisco.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/Furnex-Pelham-Village-hall-1-768x511.jpg 768w, https://www.arcdisco.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/Furnex-Pelham-Village-hall-1-1024x682.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.arcdisco.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/Tudor-Oaks-Hitchin-1.jpg\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-513\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-513 size-medium\" title=\"Tudor Oaks Hitchin\" src=\"https://www.arcdisco.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/Tudor-Oaks-Hitchin-1-300x200.jpg\" alt=\"Tudor Oaks Hitchin 1\" width=\"300\" height=\"200\" srcset=\"https://www.arcdisco.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/Tudor-Oaks-Hitchin-1-300x200.jpg 300w, https://www.arcdisco.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/Tudor-Oaks-Hitchin-1-768x511.jpg 768w, https://www.arcdisco.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/Tudor-Oaks-Hitchin-1-1024x682.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" /></a></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>• All of our bookings are confirmed in writing and issue contracts to all our clients<br />\n• Our equipment is modern, well maintained and tested for electrical saftey (P.A.T)<br />\n• Lists of your favourite tunes, to be played at your party, are welcome.<br />\n• Requests will be accepted on the night (with your permission)<br />\n• iIn addition we aim to reply to all e-mails within a 24 hour period and always return your phone calls</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.arcdisco.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/Bishops-Stortford-football-club.jpg\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-460\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-460 size-medium\" title=\"Bishops Stortford football club\" src=\"https://www.arcdisco.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/Bishops-Stortford-football-club-300x225.jpg\" alt=\"Bishops Stortford football club\" width=\"300\" height=\"225\" srcset=\"https://www.arcdisco.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/Bishops-Stortford-football-club-300x225.jpg 300w, https://www.arcdisco.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/Bishops-Stortford-football-club-768x576.jpg 768w, https://www.arcdisco.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/Bishops-Stortford-football-club-1024x768.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" /></a></p>\n<p>We carry a wide variety of music from the 50&#8217;s to the present day. If you have any special musical requests these should be made clear at the time of booking to avoid disappointment.<br />\nIf you need a disco that will play the kind of music you want to hear then call&nbsp;us.</p>\n<p>Book A.R.C. Disco and we won&#8217;t let you down,&nbsp;we do not hire other Dj&#8217;s to do events we are booked for.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.arcdisco.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/Soham-Colledge-Prom.jpg\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-495\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-495 size-medium\" title=\"Soham Colledge Prom\" src=\"https://www.arcdisco.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/Soham-Colledge-Prom-300x225.jpg\" alt=\"Soham Colledge Prom\" width=\"300\" height=\"225\" srcset=\"https://www.arcdisco.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/Soham-Colledge-Prom-300x225.jpg 300w, https://www.arcdisco.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/Soham-Colledge-Prom.jpg 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Remember that it&#8217;s YOUR function &#8230;&#8230;<br />\n&#8230;&#8230;&#8230;&#8230;we do!</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.djmark.org/member?id=13039\"><img class=\"aligncenter\" src=\"http://www.djmark.org/award?id=13039\" alt=\"\"></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.djmark.org/member?id=13039\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img class=\"aligncenter\" style=\"border: none;\" src=\"http://www.djmark.org/validator?id=13039&amp;what=pat&amp;size=400\" alt=\"\"></a><a href=\"http://www.djmark.org/member?id=13039\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img class=\"aligncenter\" style=\"border: none;\" src=\"http://www.djmark.org/validator?id=13039&amp;what=HS&amp;size=400\" alt=\"\"></a><a href=\"http://www.djmark.org/member?id=13039\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img class=\"aligncenter\" style=\"border: none;\" src=\"http://www.djmark.org/validator?id=13039&amp;what=feedback&amp;size=400\" alt=\"\"></a><a href=\"http://www.djmark.org/member?id=13039\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img class=\"aligncenter\" style=\"border: none;\" src=\"http://www.djmark.org/validator?id=13039&amp;what=pli&amp;size=400\" alt=\"\"></a></p>\n","acf":{"header":[{"heading":"Parties","headerIntro":"<p>Remember that it&#8217;s your party&#8230; we do!</p>\n<p>Tel: <a href=\"tel:+441279503870\">01279 503 870</a> • Mob: <a href=\"tel:+447956603942\">07956 603 942</a> • E-mail: <a href=\"mailto:info@arcdisco.co.uk\">info@arcdisco.co.uk</a></p>\n"}],"banners":[]}}},"context":{"path":"/pages/parties"}}